      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Karsten Müller</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"/File:Mueller_karsten_20061005_berlin_dbmm.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Mueller_karsten_20061005_berlin_dbmm.jpg/250px-Mueller_karsten_20061005_berlin_dbmm.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"260\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Mueller_karsten_20061005_berlin_dbmm.jpg/500px-Mueller_karsten_20061005_berlin_dbmm.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Mueller_karsten_20061005_berlin_dbmm.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Karsten Müller <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Karsten Müller</b>,<br />\na German mathematician, Ph.D. in 2002 from <a href=\"/University_of_Hamburg\" title=\"University of Hamburg\">University of Hamburg</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grandmaster_%28chess%29\">chess grandmaster</a> and authority in <a href=\"/Endgame\" title=\"Endgame\">chess endgames</a>. As chess columnist and writer, he is affiliated with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ChessCafe.com\">ChessCafe</a> and <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase</a>, and further authored various articles in the <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal</a>. \nHis interests apart from chess include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_game\">mathematical games</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#ChessBase_Articles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">ChessBase Articles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.althofer.de/workshop-2008.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Einpacken.jpg\" src=\"/images/a/af/Einpacken.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"359\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Eiko_Bleicher\" title=\"Eiko Bleicher\">Eiko Bleicher</a>, <a href=\"/Frank_Schneider\" title=\"Frank Schneider\">Frank Schneider</a>, <a href=\"/Chrilly_Donninger\" title=\"Chrilly Donninger\">Chrilly Donninger</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Lamprecht\">Frank Lamprecht</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Secrets of Pawn Endings</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Everyman_Chess\">Everyman Chess</a>,  (<b>2007</b>). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dev.jeremysilman.com/shop/pc/Secrets-of-Pawn-Endings-p3748.htm\">re-issue</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gambit_Publications\">Gambit Publications</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Lamprecht\">Frank Lamprecht</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.gambitbooks.com/books/Fundamental_Chess_Endings.html\">Fundamental Chess Endings</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gambit_Publications\">Gambit Publications</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://shop.chessbase.com/de/authors/cd_meyer\">Claus Dieter Meyer</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>The Magic of Chess Tactics</i>. Russell Enterprises</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>The Clash of the Titans: Kramnik – Fritz Bahrain</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Kramnik_versus_Deep_Fritz_2002\" title=\"Kramnik versus Deep Fritz 2002\">Kramnik versus Deep Fritz 2002</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ilk.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content26-1.htm#MANEQUALS\">Man Equals Machine in Chess</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#26_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 26, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Kasparov_versus_Deep_Junior_2003\" title=\"Kasparov versus Deep Junior 2003\">Kasparov versus Deep Junior 2003</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i>Endgame Corner - The Mystical Sister Squares</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chesscafe.com/text/mueller38.pdf\">pdf</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ChessCafe.com\">ChessCafe.com</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=4622170\">Wolfgang Pajeken</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>How to Play Chess Endings</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gambit_Publications\">Gambit Publications</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.russell-enterprises.com/russell-enterprises/bobby-fischer-the-career-and-complete-games-of-the-american-world-chess-champion\">Bobby Fischer - The Career and Complete Games of the American World Chess Champion</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.russell-enterprises.com/\">Russell Enterprises</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://centaur.reading.ac.uk/36189/\">Rook vs. Bishop</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 4</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Tablebases, Fermat, Knights and Knightmares</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#39_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 39, No. 2</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.russell-enterprises.com/russell-enterprises/man-vs-machinebrchallenging-human-supremacy-at-chess\">Man vs. Machine: Challenging Human Supremacy at Chess</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.russell-enterprises.com/\">Russell Enterprises</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Chess Endgame News: The World Chess Championship, 2018</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 4</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>FinalGen revisited: new discoveries</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#41_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 41, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/FinalGen\" title=\"FinalGen\">FinalGen</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>Stalemate and ‘DTS’ depth to stalemate endgame tables</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#41_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 41, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/Stalemate\" title=\"Stalemate\">Stalemate</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"ChessBase_Articles\">ChessBase Articles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: ChessBase Articles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.chessbase.com/post/historical-riddle-could-kramnik-have-defeated-the-computer\">Historical riddle: could Kramnik have defeated the computer?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase News</a>, May 28, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Kramnik_versus_Deep_Fritz_2006\" title=\"Kramnik versus Deep Fritz 2006\">Kramnik versus Deep Fritz 2006</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.chessbase.com/post/solution-to-the-historical-riddle-kramnik-could-have-defeated-fritz\">Solution to the historical riddle: Kramnik could have defeated Fritz!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karsten Müller</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase News</a>, June 01, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karsten_M%C3%BCller\">Karsten Müller from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=4600347\">Mueller, Karsten, Dr. FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/perl/chessplayer?pid=11726\">The chess games of Karsten Mueller</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karsten_M%C3%BCller&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Karsten Müller at the 6th German companies team chess championship, October 05, 2006, Berlin, Photo by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benutzer:Frank_Hoppe\">Frank Hoppe</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karsten_M%C3%BCller\">Karsten Müller from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karsten_M%C3%BCller\">Karsten Müller from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.althofer.de/workshop-2008.html\">Workshop Jena 2008: Analysis, Design, and Programming of Games</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.schachversand.de/de/mueller,_karsten-buch-englisch.html\">Müller, Karsten - Books</a>, <a href=\"/Schachversand_Niggemann\" title=\"Schachversand Niggemann\">Schachversand Niggemann</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/m/M=uuml=ller_0006:Karsten\">dblp: Karsten Müller 0006</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Chess_Championship_2018\">World Chess Championship 2018 from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301102530\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.627 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 115/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 242/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTem